{"tid":1726271,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post，和理非無限期三罷]真罷工呼籲---先行者","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T01:50:02.000Z","uid":89974,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1b24b8522d0379e54ef4542de269e1c5751bdf87","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC發佈：<br />\n<br />\n我地係一群願意承擔被解僱風險，敢於向公司發聲，以及敢於身體力行的手足。現希望召募同路人作為罷工的先行隊伍，討論和執行罷工的具體行動及相關宣傳，並於社會製造聲音和豎立榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n何為先行隊伍? 我們知道已有不同界別開始討論罷工的事宜。<br />\n罷工的事宜並非一朝一夕可以達成，實在需要時間醞釀。不同行業各有難處，參與者亦有各自的考慮及顧慮。<br />\n因此我們希望可以召集一眾願意承擔風險，勇於罷工的人士，意在率先在社會製造聲音。<br />\n<br />\n運動至今已數個月，政府依舊以「回應」不是「答應」的態度來回應民意，依舊利用警隊以暴力鎮壓各種示威活動，依舊製造和允許各樣白色恐怖，而非利用政治智慧解決問題。我等希望各位能夠以罷工的形式逼令政府妥協，行使基本法賦予我們的權利。<br />\n<br />\n重申：工會與基金既路線已經有人做緊(感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，所以我地唔會談任何工會及基金問題，並會轉介到你去大公海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭像 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所有</span>願意響應罷工，無論是先行者，或者之後愈多人罷愈願意罷工的同路人，一齊在社交媒體同步轉支持罷工的frame pic，從表態做起，表達罷工人浪到底有幾大：<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33Syr1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33Syr1g&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=c4f75d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33Syr1g</a><br />\nFacebook(英文版)：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rPhVRH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rPhVRH&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=195f8be4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rPhVRH</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp, Instagram, Telegram：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCO4HD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCO4HD1.jpg&h=90dc67f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4KPdLq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4KPdLq.jpg&h=f1280373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召募身邊同事</span></span><br />\n工會形成罷工係最正統既做法，但係其實小隊形式罷工亦值得一試！如果你既工種難請人，替換度低，而又有機會同一個department同時罷工，其實壓力不亞於一個工會罷工！<br />\n旁敲側擊你身邊的黃色同事，叫佢睇晒成篇罷工Q&amp;A(不定時更新)<br />\n<br />\n一個人的力量有限，一群人的力量就是無限！我地需要你！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理念請仔細睇Q &amp; A ︰</span></span> <br />\n<br />\nQ1︰罷工算唔算和理非？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA1 ︰罷工係暴力之外，亦即係和理非既最終手段！政府管治既係社會而非死物，所以只要將社會癱瘓，民不聊生，政府將會逼於無奈妥協！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ2︰可唔可以「被罷工」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA2 ︰因為「被罷工」而返唔到工，果D叫做比老闆扣大假或者出No Pay Leave，最多叫多日假，一點壓力都比唔到政府！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ3︰點樣先算「真。罷工」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA3︰當我地擁有一定人數既敢炒隊時，集體寫封信比你老闆話佢知，你罷工係要令香港停擺，迫政府回應五大訴求！到時我地將會有範文參考！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ4︰都未有工會/保障基金，點罷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA4︰首先工會同基金已經搞緊，但實在追唔上局勢惡化既進度！如果你係為咗薪金，為咗福利，咁樣大台的確係有必要，因為咁先可以確保你唔會俾資方針對；然而而家已經係生死存亡之際，大屠殺隨時來臨，各區充滿毒氣，無論你係為咗信念，健康定係安全，你都應該隨時準備罷工！二噁英並唔會理你係番工定係唔番工，你都會同樣中毒！我地已經去到種族滅絕既最後關頭，就只差臨門一腳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\nQ5︰可唔可以一個行業或一間公司咁發動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA5︰可以！但唔一定要！如果你公司有幾個志同道合嘅義士，一齊SEND罷工宣言就更好，被炒機會大大減低，最好同一個部門，你公司無可能即刻代替你地！威力更大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ6︰一個強大的罷工行動要咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA6︰首先要有唔怕無得撈嘅第一梯隊，然後要有會跟進嘅第二、第三梯隊，只要多D人走出宣佈罷工就會成功！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ7︰點算成功罷工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA7︰社會癱瘓，香港死城，直到政府回應五大訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後言：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，行先死先，罷先炒先，我地需要「敢炒隊」做第一梯隊，先行帶起呢場行動！當見到八大學生同前線浴血奮戰，當見到無數年青人屍體浮現，你敢唔敢下定決心第一個走出嚟「真。罷工」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家按自己能力入群！同時我們亦更加容易聯合到相同處境既人士！<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: blue;\">第一梯隊：</span>如果你願意做罷工敢炒隊，請去呢度：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/353CbNN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F353CbNN&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=e8a0e7e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/353CbNN</a><br />\n2.<span style=\"color: teal;\">第二梯隊：</span>如果你公司有人做敢炒隊就會跟住罷工，請入呢度︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37bMbXd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37bMbXd&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=20cde4f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37bMbXd</a><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: navy;\">高層級：</span>如果你有能力組織到一個部門、一間鋪、甚至一間公司嘅罷工，請入呢度︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QkbcJL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QkbcJL&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=72bcc1b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QkbcJL</a><br />\n4.如果真係有好多人罷工/要有工會先罷工請入呢度︰<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=c29ec2ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n5.如果你只想得知最新消息請去公海︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rHLbJV&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=296da63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港需要你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0d4d1c5deb8f0781d3ea1c7bcd6e4867c2ae248f","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13239aecdac3b2713447a7a240e337a115897fe4","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feea395f89dc4700d60f1d1ad8aa43994ed4d386","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603fdd1175c09114c8ffacbee8f78f9a4e508999","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4736b45fd81ec2c0bdcb331a55c8b7cf55814f","tid":1726271,"uid":157436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"60005ab812acd66e88947b0d69d9de727d53517d","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1bf365b7759fa32f38491da73e83ea61cf3131","tid":1726271,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=c90a07f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXrvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=871ed266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"c84a9977cbabbb6f75dbca4ab7f464ecc35109a5","tid":1726271,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif